---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Spacetime Continuum of Sound" description="Spacetime Continuum of Sound by Farfama" />
		<style>

			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				display: flex;
				font-size: 14px;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				min-height: 100vh;

			}
			.content {
				flex-grow: 1;
				padding: 60px;
				max-width: 800px;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.game-section {
				margin-bottom: 60px;
			}
			.game-title {
				font-size: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;


			}
			
			.image-gallery {
				display: flex;
				overflow-x: auto;
				gap: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
			}
			.gallery-item {
				flex: 0 0 auto;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 533px;
				height: 300px;
			}
			.gallery-video {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			.gallery-image {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.game-description {
				max-width: 600px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;
				white-space: pre-wrap;

			}
			.game-credits {
				margin-top: 12px;
				max-width: 600px;
			}
			.game-credits ul {
				margin: 4px 0 0 0;
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				body {
					flex-direction: column;
				}
				.content {
					padding: 20px;
				}
				.game-title {
					font-size: 20px;
				}
				.gallery-item {
					height: 56.25vw; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
					max-height: 300px;
				}
				.game-description {
					font-size: 14px;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Sidebar />
		<div class="content">
            <p>
            Spacetime Continuum of Sound is an interactive audio-visual experience that explores the relationship between sound and space. Created by Farfama, this project invites users to immerse themselves in a dynamic environment where soundscapes evolve based on user interactions. 
            The experience is designed to challenge perceptions of time and space, offering a unique journey through auditory landscapes.
</p>
            <p>
            The project utilizes advanced audio processing techniques to create a responsive sound environment. As users navigate through the space, they encounter various sound elements that react to their movements and actions, creating a personalized auditory experience. 
            The visual component complements the soundscapes, providing a cohesive and engaging experience that stimulates both the senses of hearing and sight.
</p>
            <p>
            Spacetime Continuum of Sound is a testament to Farfama's commitment to pushing the boundaries of interactive media. By blending technology, art, and sound design, this project offers a compelling exploration of how sound can shape our perception of space and time. It is an invitation to explore the unknown and to experience the transformative power of sound in a new and innovative way.
</p>    
		</div>
	</body>
</html>